      • GrammarConfig

        public GrammarConfig(String grammar,
                     int max_ts,
                     double ch_vs_rep,
                     int num_vars,
                     double min_node_grow,
                     double max_node_grow,
                     boolean is_prop_pnodes,
                     int max_gd,
                     double tm_vs_ntm)
        Parameters:
        grammar - the grammar
        max_ts - set the maximum allowed tree size
        ch_vs_rep - the change versus replace ration from the range [0,1]
        num_vars - the number of variables
        min_node_grow - the minimum node grow coefficient
        max_node_grow - the maximum node grow coefficient
        is_prop_pnodes - true if placement nodes are to be propagated
        max_gd - the maximum grammar depth for fixed point iteration
        tm_vs_ntm - terminal versus non terminal mutation ratio
